  "title": "BEAUTICIAN",
  "description": "<p><strong>✨ Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Provide beauty treatments such as facial, waxing, threading, manicure/pedicure, and basic makeup.</p></li><li><p>Recommend skincare and beauty products to clients.</p></li><li><p>Maintain cleanliness and hygiene of salon tools and work areas.</p></li><li><p>Deliver excellent customer service and ensure client satisfaction.</p></li></ul><p><strong>💄 Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Proven experience as a Beautician or similar role.</p></li><li><p>Skilled in facial, waxing, and basic beauty services.</p></li><li><p>Good communication and interpersonal skills.</p></li><li><p>Positive attitude and team player.</p></li><li><p>Relevant beauty certifications preferred.</p></li></ul>",
